thread.title_full: Lady Gaga is dating CAA talent agent Christian Carino | Daily Mail Online

author: Chelsea White For Dailymail.com
title: is dating CAA talent agent Christian Carino
text:
While no doubt her ex Taylor Kinney is hoping this will be a Bad Romance, it seems singer has found someone to be the glue to help mend her broken heart.
Less than a week after Lady Gaga was spotted cozying up to a man for a sexy selfie ahead of her Super Bowl performance his identity has been revealed.
The 30-year-old is reportedly dating CAA talent agent Christian Carino, 48, according to People.
New couple alert: Lady Gaga is reportedly dating CAA talent agent Christian Carino (pictured here Sunday)
A source confirmed the pair were more than just selfie buddies on Thursday.
Christian was seen giving the Love Game singer a kiss on the cheek as she snapped away on the field before Sunday's Super Bowl.
According to People's insider, the pair were also seen getting affectionate at a Kings of Leon concert.
Christian was also seen with the star at Wednesday night's Tommy X Gigi fashion Show in Venice, California. Christian is longtime friends of designer Tommy Hilfiger.
By her side: Christian was seen giving the Love Game singer a kiss on the cheek as she snapped away on the field before Sunday's Super Bowl
Hold my bag: Christian (rear) was also seen with the star at Wednesday night's Tommy X Gigi fashion Show in Venice, California. Christian is longtime friends of designer Tommy Hilfiger
It seems the pop star is already close to the agent's family, as she took a girl whom looked a lot like Christian's daughter Bella to the show with her.
The star and the teen sat front row during the show and left holding hands.
The 48-year-old talent agent looks after the commercial and sponsorship interests of Justin Bieber, Amber Heard, Christina Aguilera, Simon Cowell, Miley Cyrus and Jennifer Lopez.

He previously dated Walking Dead’s Lauren Cohan as of late last year.
This is the first time Gaga has been linked to a man since she called off her engagement to Taylor Kinney.
The singer and her 35-year-old ex-fiance called off their engagement in July.
Ex files: The agent previously dated Walking Dead’s Lauren Cohan as of late last year (pictured here in November)
Moving on: This is the first time Gaga has been linked to a man since she called off her engagement to Taylor Kinney (pictured January 2016) last July
Taylor had proposed on Valentine's Day in 2015 after the pair were together for four years.
Gaga at the time did not rule out reuniting with her partner of five years saying: 'Taylor and I have always believed we are soulmates. Just like all couples we have ups and downs, and we have been taking a break.
'We are both ambitious artists, hoping to work through long-distance and complicated schedules to continue the simple love we have always shared.'
